Ordered.documentation: Ancestor of types with total order relation defined, i.e. '<' and '='.
Ordered.name: Ordered

Interval.documentation: Type defining an interval of any ordered type.
Interval.name: Interval

Hash.documentation: Type defining Hash table / hash map structure, whose type parameters V and K represent a value type and an Ordered key type respectively.
Hash.name: Hash

ISO8601_DATE.documentation: Date type based on IS8601 representation.
ISO8601_DATE.name: ISO8601_DATE

ISO8601_TIME.documentation: Time type based on IS8601 representation.
ISO8601_TIME.name: ISO8601_TIME

ISO8601_DATE_TIME.documentation: Date Time type based on IS8601 representation.
ISO8601_DATE_TIME.name: ISO8601_DATE_TIME

ISO8601_DURATION.documentation: Duration type based on IS8601 representation.
ISO8601_DURATION.name: ISO8601_DURATION
